                        d="M13 17H11M6.38 18A7.95 7.95 0 0 0 12 20C15.866 20 19 16.866 19 13A7.95 7.95 0 0 0 19.74 11H4.67A7.95 7.95 0 0 0 5 13C5 15.7614 7.23858 18 10 18Z">
